{"tid":2310563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"塞車五分鐘，離島人坐立不安，起哄；官塘人unun腳","createTime":"2020-12-03T10:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T14:35:12.000Z","uid":367147,"like":91,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4872a73115172bb5a05efc5e15c5e1ccd0df2a","tid":2310563,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"塞車十分鐘，半山富豪call直升機；官塘人在車上看風景。<br />\n塞車半小時，太古人準備揸遊艇過海；官塘廢老在巴士剪指甲。<br />\n塞車一小時，將軍澳人不停響咹，試圖用聲波振走死車；官塘人繼續打機。<br />\n塞車三小時，荃灣人準備落車行路返工；官塘人開始望望出面發生咩事。<br />\n塞車一日，旺角人失控𠝹櫈；官塘人擪定尿片，等待真正的塞車到來。<br />\n塞車一星期，紅隧人昏迷，但無白車入到；官塘人抱怨車上沒有糧食。<br />\n塞車一年，屯公的車已變廢鐵，開始腐爛；官塘人終於說：『老天，外面好塞！』<br />\n住屯門返官塘人：『最近條路開始塞車了！』<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105280438066232/posts/117071676887108/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105280438066232%2Fposts%2F117071676887108%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=a39fda3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105280438066232/posts/117071676887108/</a>"},{"pid":"d02be04f2767ef5b4a00a287f69e50a6e5d9ba87","tid":2310563,"uid":89046,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXUfaay.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXUfaay.gif&h=769b643d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"103fc28d7942be7b2c160606c21a1a3b940155cf","tid":2310563,"uid":150902,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3R6owFJ9qHA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3R6owFJ9qHA&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=635d4424\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3R6owFJ9qHA</a>"},{"pid":"c3d370d80c56389